com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.fingerprint.FirstOrderNonLinearFingerprintPositionEstimator2D
public class FirstOrderNonLinearFingerprintPositionEstimator2D extends NonLinearFingerprintPositionEstimator2D
2D position estimator based on located fingerprints containing only RSSI readings and having as well prior knowledge of the location of radio sources associated to those readings. This implementation uses a first-order Taylor approximation over provided located fingerprints to determine an approximate position for a non-located fingerprint using a non-linear solving algorithm. An initial position can be provided as a starting point to solve the position, otherwise the average point of selected nearest fingerprints is used as a starting point.
